title: OBJ, Dak Prescott, NCAA, NFL attendance
itunes:title: OBJ, Dak Prescott, NCAA, NFL attendance
description:
Colin discusses the rumored Odell Beckham Jr. trade, why Dak Prescott is upset with the Cowboys, the possibility of colleges trimming some programs, and why the NFL having games with no fans would be fine. Guests include Nick Wright, Greg Jennings, Michael Pittman, and Mike Renner.
